commit.message:
Merge pull request #11 from pyrocko/master

Added support for Google Web Fonts
Added support for Google Web Fonts
Fix regression in sidebar size when there was no page content. Sidebar has its own height again.
Fix sidebar contents not moving while scrolling at all.

Avoid !important in CSS

One instance is still there, because I don't know what it does and if
it is necessary.

See #9.
Fix display of paragraphs in table cells. Fix display of "p" anchors (that have id and got :target).
Fix display of argument descriptions when there are multiple paragraphs.
Fixed issues with highlighting a section (via anchor location hash). Previously code blocks would get ugly bar on the left.
Don't install anything in these envs (builds faster).
Fix sidebar display in narrow media. Closes #8.
